        public OctreeNode(int minimumObjectsPerNode,
          int maximumObjectsPerNode,
          Vector3 center,
          float dimension)
        Create a new octree
        Parameters:
        minimumObjectsPerNode - The minimum number of objects held before merging nodes
        maximumObjectsPerNode - The maximum number of objects in a node before splitting May be exceeded due to objects not insertable into child nodes
        center - Center of this octree
        dimension - Size of the octree in each direction
